schools.name: Boerne - Samuel V Champion High School

data.description: Come see this beautiful and spacious 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bath home in the lovely town of Boerne TX. Open floor plan with granite counter tops, gas stove, huge 2nd living area upstairs, spacious master bedroom with double vanity master bath and separate tub & shower. This energy efficient home comes with a radiant barrier roof. Backyard with covered patio backs up to a green belt behind Boerne Middle School South. Transferable 10 year builder warranty. Contact your agent for a showing today!
data.whatILove: We love the small town feel of living in Boerne, but we also have easy access to go to San Antonio.
